OL,3,C'The shelling took away my whole
OL,4,Cfamily'
OL,6,F"Without warning, an Israeli airstrike
OL,7,Fsmashed into Maha's building.
OL,9,F"I stood up after the bombing...
OL,10,Flooked around... nothing. No walls. No
OL,11,Fpeople.
OL,13,F"I started screaming their names... my
OL,14,Fchildren, Mum, Dad, my brother's name,
OL,15,Fmy sisters'.... no one answered.
OL,17,FThat's when I realised they were all
OL,18,Fgone."
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/9
