OL,3,C'The shelling took away my whole
OL,4,Cfamily'
OL,6,FStunned and in shock, still screaming
OL,7,Fthe names of her family, Maha started
OL,8,Fheading downstairs.
OL,10,F"While I was going down the stairs, I
OL,11,Flooked at the next building... I saw
OL,12,Fmy son!
OL,14,F"I felt alive again."
OL,16,FMaha's seven-year-old son Ali Faraj
OL,17,Fhad been thrown from the fifth floor
OL,18,Fto the third floor of the next
OL,19,Fbuilding.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/9
