OL,4,Cfamily'
OL,6,F"My daughters were shredded."
OL,8,FA rescue team managed to get Maha's
OL,9,Fson Ali, and both were taken to
OL,10,Fhospital.
OL,12,F"I had burns on my back and arm", says
OL,13,FMaha.
OL,15,F"At the hospital I feared no one else
OL,16,Fhad survived. I asked if anyone else
OL,17,Fmade it.
OL,19,F"They told me: just me and my son."
