OL,6,FMaha's husband and five daughters,
OL,7,Faged between 2 and 14, had been killed
OL,8,Fin the blast.
OL,10,F"I had a little daughter. She was just
OL,11,Ftwo years old. She used to sing to me:
OL,12,F'My mum, my mum, I love my mum.'
OL,14,F"Who will sing that to me now?"
OL,16,FIn a statement given to ITV News, the
OL,17,FIDF said: "On Thursday, April the
OL,18,F24th, the Israeli Air Force struck a
OL,19,FHamas terrorist in Gaza City.
