OL,6,F"Prior to the strike, steps were taken
OL,7,Fto mitigate potential harm to
OL,8,Fcivilians including the use of precise
OL,9,Fmunitions, aerial surveillance and
OL,10,Fadditional intelligence."
OL,12,FITV News believes the bombing killed
OL,13,F19 people, 15 of whom were women and
OL,14,Fchildren.
OL,16,F"I don't have a home anymore," says
OL,17,FMaha. "When the war ends, I still
OL,18,Fwon't have a home. I'm alone".
OL,20,FDespite everything, Maha is grateful
OL,21,Fthat Ali survives.
